  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dark Crescent is a roguelike deck builder with an unique twist. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Procedurally Generated Battles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3541730/extras/52df35f55bf109edfaec44ab266b54d5.poster.avif?t=1741967954\" width=800 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3541730/extras/52df35f55bf109edfaec44ab266b54d5.webm?t=1741967954\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3541730/extras/52df35f55bf109edfaec44ab266b54d5.mp4?t=1741967954\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight your way through increasingly difficult encounters. Face powerful enemies and bosses on your journey towards the moon. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Recruit Your Foes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3541730/extras/3103a39bb46b2524a86f10b5c85dafee.poster.avif?t=1741967954\" width=800 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3541730/extras/3103a39bb46b2524a86f10b5c85dafee.webm?t=1741967954\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3541730/extras/3103a39bb46b2524a86f10b5c85dafee.mp4?t=1741967954\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The last enemy slain will offer his services to you. Will you accept? </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Discover Powerful Artifacts</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3541730/extras/5e505ad44f245bc14acdb143ae4e3d96.poster.avif?t=1741967954\" width=800 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3541730/extras/5e505ad44f245bc14acdb143ae4e3d96.webm?t=1741967954\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3541730/extras/5e505ad44f245bc14acdb143ae4e3d96.mp4?t=1741967954\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip each member of your team with unique boons to alter your playstyle. But beware, as curses are inevitable. </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dark Crescent is a roguelike deck builder with an unique twist. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Procedurally Generated Battles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3541730/extras/52df35f55bf109edfaec44ab266b54d5.poster.avif?t=1741967954\" width=800 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3541730/extras/52df35f55bf109edfaec44ab266b54d5.webm?t=1741967954\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3541730/extras/52df35f55bf109edfaec44ab266b54d5.mp4?t=1741967954\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight your way through increasingly difficult encounters. Face powerful enemies and bosses on your journey towards the moon. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Recruit Your Foes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3541730/extras/3103a39bb46b2524a86f10b5c85dafee.poster.avif?t=1741967954\" width=800 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3541730/extras/3103a39bb46b2524a86f10b5c85dafee.webm?t=1741967954\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3541730/extras/3103a39bb46b2524a86f10b5c85dafee.mp4?t=1741967954\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The last enemy slain will offer his services to you. Will you accept? </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Discover Powerful Artifacts</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3541730/extras/5e505ad44f245bc14acdb143ae4e3d96.poster.avif?t=1741967954\" width=800 height=600 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3541730/extras/5e505ad44f245bc14acdb143ae4e3d96.webm?t=1741967954\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3541730/extras/5e505ad44f245bc14acdb143ae4e3d96.mp4?t=1741967954\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equip each member of your team with unique boons to alter your playstyle. But beware, as curses are inevitable. </p>",
